snippet.title: Titanfall 2 Teaser Trailer – PS4, Xbox One and PC
snippet.description:
Be among the first to discover Titanfall 2: http://x.ea.com/4009

From Respawn Entertainment™, the studio that brought you the award-winning Titanfall™, comes Titanfall™ 2. 

Subscribe to see the first Titanfall 2 gameplay trailer coming June 12: http://x.ea.com/4122

Titanfall 2 will be available on PS4, Xbox One, and PC.
